武汉之外湖北多地医用物资告急：口罩最缺，根本买不到。
Wuhan outside Hubei many medical supplies are in urgent need: Mask is most lacking, can not buy at all.
王昱倩 张静雅。
Yue Wang Zhang Jingya.
