咸宁市第一人民医院现有防护物资仅能维持一天，襄阳市中医医院防护服已告罄，N95口罩需消毒再利用，汉川市人民医院的橡胶手套快要消耗完。
Xiangning First People's Hospital can only last one day, Xiangyang City Chinese Medicine Hospital protective clothing has been exhausted, N95 masks need disinfection and reuse, Hanchuan City People's Hospital rubber gloves are nearly exhausted.
全文2306字，阅读约需5分钟1月26日，来自湖北省多地的数家医院向新京报记者证实，目前医疗防护物资已告急。
Chinese hospitals in many parts of Hubei province confirmed to the Beijing News that medical supplies are in urgent need of medical care.
它们纷纷向社会发出捐赠公告。
They have issued public announcements of donations.
湖北省卫健委发布的消息称，截至1月25日24时，湖北省累计报告新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎确诊病例1052例，其中武汉市618例，黄冈市122例，孝感市55例，咸宁市43例。
As of 2400 hours January 25, 1,052 confirmed cases of pneumonia with a new coronavirus infection had been reported in Hubei Province, including 618 in Wuhan, 122 in Huanggang, 55 in Xiaogan City and 43 in Xianning, Hubei Province, according to a report released by the Hubei Wei Boxing Commission.
武汉之外，湖北省其余市州的防疫状况日益受到关注。
In addition to Wuhan, the epidemic prevention situation in the remaining cities of Hubei Province has attracted increasing attention.
新京报记者了解到，孝感、咸宁、恩施、襄阳等多地医院的防护物资均告急，咸宁市第一人民医院现有防护物资仅能维持一天，襄阳市中医医院防护服已告罄，N95口罩需消毒再利用，汉川市人民医院的橡胶手套快要消耗完。
Newspaper Beijing News learned that filial piety, Xianning, Enshi, Xiangyang hospitals and other protective materials are in urgent need, Xianning City First People's Hospital can only last one day, Xiangyang City Chinese Medicine Hospital protective clothing has been exhausted, N95 masks need disinfection and reuse, Hanchuan People's Hospital rubber gloves are running out.
━━━━━孝感：口罩、面罩紧缺孝感市中心医院的工作人员告诉新京报记者，医院现在最紧缺的是防护服、N95口罩，一天的需求量是300件。
Filial piety Feel the Feeling Feel the Feel the Feel the Feel the Feel the Feel the Feel the Feel the Feel the Feel the Feel the Feel the Feel the Feel Feel the Feel the Feel Feel the Feel Feel the Feel the Feel Feel the Feel Feel the Feel Feel the Feel the Feel Feel the Feel Feel the Feel the Feel Feel the Feel Feel the Feel the Feel Feel the Feel Feel the Feel the Feel Feel the Feel Feel the Feel Feel the Feel the Feel the Feel the Feel the Feel the Feel the Feel the Feel Feel the Feel the Feel the Feel the Feel Feel the Feel the Feel the Feel the Feel the Feel Feel the Feel
1月24日晚上医院发出捐赠公告，1月26日已经收到了为数不多的防护服，勉强维持四、五天的用量，但是依旧没有N95口罩和面罩，眼罩也是极少量的存货。
The hospital issued a donation announcement on the evening of 24 January and received a limited number of protective clothing on 26 January, barely enough to last four or five days, but still without N95 masks and masks and with minuscule eye coverings.
▲孝感市中心医院的捐赠公告。
Xiaogan City Central Hospital donation announcement.
受访者供图孝感市第一人民医院的工作人员亦称，口罩特别短缺，起步需求量是1万个，之后的需求量还会增长，要看收治病人的数量。
Respondents also said there was a special shortage of face masks, with a demand of 10,000, and that demand would increase after that depending on the number of patients admitted.
▲孝感市第一人民医院的捐赠公告。
Xiaogan City First People's Hospital donation announcement.
受访者供图━━━━━咸宁第一人民医院：需要5000个N95口罩咸宁市中心医院的工作人员称，他们目前对N95口罩的需求量是5000个，防护面罩是一两千个，防护服还有维持半个月的数量：“前几天已经有人给我们寄了顺丰快递，但不知什么原因，目前都没收到。
2007-9-24 16: 16 [hide] Xianning People's Hospital: 5,000 N95 masks are now in demand, 1,000 face masks are in use, and the number of protective clothing will last half a month: "Shun Fung Express was sent to us a few days ago, but for some reason, we haven't received it yet.
目前我们的医护人员暂时比较安全，但人都很疲劳。
At present, our medical staff is relatively safe for the time being, but people are very tired.
”▲咸宁市中心医院的捐赠公告。
"Xianning City Central Hospital donation announcement.
受访者供图咸宁市第一人民医院的工作人员向新京报记者提供的带有公章的紧急求助书显示，目前该医院现有的防护物资仅能维持1天，很多医护人员防护不加，急需社会各界捐赠。
An emergency appeal with an official seal for staff of the No. 1 People's Hospital in Tuangning City showed that the hospital currently has only one day's supply of protective materials, and many medical workers are unprotected and in urgent need of donations from the public.
该医院的工作人员告诉新京报记者，现在最缺口罩，已经募捐到一部分，但现在都卡在路上没有收到。
Staff at the hospital told the Beijing News that the shortfall, which has been partially funded, is now stuck on the road and not received.
▲咸宁市第一人民医院的紧急求助及捐助需求单。
Xianning City First People's Hospital emergency help and donor needs list.
受访者供图“以15天的用量计算，N95口罩、医用外科口罩及一次性使用医用口罩各需要两万七千个，防护服、护目镜、保护面罩、乳胶手套、消毒水等各需要一万四千个，新型冠状病毒检测试剂需要1000个。
The figure shows that "Based on the 15-day dosage, 27,000 surgical masks are needed for N95 masks, surgical masks for medical use, 14,000 each for protective clothing, goggles, protective masks, latex gloves, disinfectant water, etc., and 1,000 for the new coronavirus detection reagent.
每天的消耗量很大，所以严重告急。
The daily consumption is very large, so serious emergency.
但是现在个人很难邮寄进来，需要一个厂家和快递公司对接。
But now it is difficult for individuals to mail in, and a manufacturer and express company are needed to dock.
”上述工作人员称。
"said the official.
━━━━━恩施：部分医院防护物资只能维持几天恩施州利川市人民医院的工作人员称，发捐赠公告时，防护物资只能维持三、五天了，目前陆续已经收到一些爱心人士的捐赠，口罩、护目镜、防护面罩等需求量仍在1万个左右。
Some hospital protective materials can only last for a few days, officials at the People's Hospital in Lichuan, Enshi state, said that when the announcement was made, protective materials would last only three to five days. Donations had been received from loving people, and demand for masks, goggles and face masks remained at around 10,000.
“目前医护人员情况还好，没有出现交叉感染的情况。
"There is no cross-infection at the moment," he said.
”鹤峰县是湖北省内唯一不通高速的县级市，交通不便，物资匮乏，返乡人口居多。
Hefeng County is the only county-level city in Hubei province that does not have a high speed.
鹤峰县中心医院的一位院领导告诉新京报记者，现在的医疗物资只能维持几天的用量，目前口罩、防护服都缺1万套。
Hefeng County Central Hospital, a hospital leadership told the Beijing News, the current medical supplies can only last a few days, the current shortage of masks, protective clothing are 10,000 sets.
▲鹤峰县中心医院的捐助公告。
Hefeng County Central Hospital donation announcement.
受访者供图━━━━━襄阳市中医医院：医护对口罩消毒再利用湖北省卫健委发布的通报中，黄石市、襄阳市、咸宁市为报告首例确诊病例。
2007-9-24 16: 23 [hide] Xiangyang City Chinese Medicine Hospital: Medical and Medical Mask Sterilizing and Reusing the Notices Issued by Hubei Provincial Health Committee, Huangshi City, Xiangyang City and Xianning City were the first confirmed cases reported.
新京报记者联系襄阳市的多家医院，他们称，由于从武汉返乡的人数多，他们的医疗物资十分紧缺，故亦向社会发出了捐赠公告。
The Beijing News contacted several hospitals in Xiangyang City and said the announcement was made in response to a shortage of medical supplies due to the high number of returnees from Wuhan.
“发公告时，防护服已经一件也没有了，我们现在都是穿的医院反复消毒的隔离衣，再加一层一次性手术衣。
"At the time of the announcement, we had no protective clothing at all. We were all wearing hospital disinfectant paraphernalia and a disposable surgical coat.
”襄阳市中医医院的工作人员告诉新京报记者，“今天中午统计了下，N95的口罩只剩下30副了，只能消毒了再利用。
Staff at Xiangyang TCM Hospital told the Beijing News: "This noon we counted only 30 pairs of N95 masks, which can only be sterilized and reused.
”上述工作人员表示，现在医护人员也在加班扛着，医院熬制了一些中药，发给大家喝：“由于N95的口罩每天消耗量在100到150个之间，防护服每天80套，如果按照一周的数量计算，希望能先捐到200件防护服，我们给一线直接接触病例的人用，其他人我们用普通的，这样社会各界也能捐给其他缺物资的地方使用。
"With N95 masks consumed between 100 and 150 a day and 80 suits a day, we hope to donate 200 first-line protective clothing to those in direct contact, others to others so that all sectors of society can also donate to other areas where supplies are scarce," said the staff.
”▲襄阳市中医医院的捐助公告。
"Xiangyang City Traditional Chinese Medicine Hospital donation announcement.
受访者供图另一家医院，襄阳市中心医院的工作人员称，希望得到社会的援助，目前能捐多少就捐多少，最需要N95口罩和防护服。
The interviewees told the staff at Xiangyang City Hospital, another hospital, that they wanted to receive social assistance by donating as much as they could, and needed N95 masks and protective clothing the most.
▲襄阳市中心医院的捐助公告。
Xiangyang City Hospital donation announcement.
受访者供图━━━━━汉川：N95口罩、手套紧缺汉川市人民医院的一名医生告诉新京报记者，目前医院内物资严重短缺，N95防护口罩已经一个不剩，一线的医护人员只能戴着两层医用外科口罩继续工作。
2007-9-25 21: 48 A doctor at the Hanchuan People's Hospital told the Beijing News that there was a severe shortage of materials, that N95 face masks were no longer in use and that frontline medical staff could only continue to work in two layers of medical surgical masks.
他称，医护人员均已停休，1600余人全部在岗，每天口罩的消耗量超过2000个，物资消耗严重：“现在汉川市的N95口罩已经全部断货，根本没有地方购买。
He said doctors and nurses have stopped working, 1,600 are on duty, consume more than 2,000 face masks a day and consume serious supplies: "Now all the N95 masks in Hanchuan are out of stock and there is no place to buy them.
我们最缺乏的就是这种口罩。
What we lack most is this mask.
”这名医生称，医院内的橡胶手套使用的也很快，现在存货已经快消耗完：“医护人员需要在完全封闭的情况下，对患者进行检查。
Rubber gloves were also used quickly, the doctor said, and now stocks are running low: "Health-care workers need to examine patients in complete isolation.
”他表示，目前这些物资都很难在市内买到，“我们直接去过医疗器材厂调货，但是效果并不理想。
"We have been directly to the medical equipment factory to transfer the goods, but the results have not been ideal," he said.
”这名医生称，无奈下，医院只能向社会求助，通过志愿者扩散出去，进行筹集，或通过官方慈善机构筹集。
The doctor said hospitals were forced to turn to society for help, spread out through volunteers, raise money or raise money through official charities.
此外，这名医生称，虽然向社会募捐护目镜，但是需要提示捐助者，并非所有护目镜都符合医用防护的要求。
In addition, the doctor stated that although goggles were solicited from the community, donors needed to be reminded that not all goggles met medical protection requirements.
“需要那种眼眶周围带着橡胶圈的，能够将眼睛安全与外界隔离开，以免细菌从眼部入侵。
"You need rubber bands around your eyes to keep your eyes safe from the outside world and keep them out of the way.
”▲汉川市人民医院物资需求表。
Hanchuan City People's Hospital material needs table.
受访者供图汉川市第二人民医院也面临相同的问题。
Respondents also faced the same problem at the No. 2 People's Hospital in Tuhanchuan.
“口罩最缺乏，根本买不到。
"Masks are in short supply and cannot be bought.
”一名医生告诉新京报记者，目前医护人员们格外注意，尽量减少更换的频率，但是口罩还是不够用。
A doctor told the Beijing News that doctors and nurses are taking extra care to minimize the frequency of changes, but masks are still not enough.
“像是口罩、橡胶手套以及防护服，很多都是一次性使用的，一旦反复使用，就失去了原本的功效。
"Many of these masks, rubber gloves and protective clothing are disposable and lose their effectiveness once they are used repeatedly.
”这名医生称，目前医院也在自己想办法，但效果并不好：“断货太严重，和厂商问，他们也说不清到底什么时候能够有货。
The doctor said the hospital was doing its own thing, but the effect was not good: "The outages were so severe that the manufacturer asked when they would be able to have them.
”新京报记者 王昱倩 张静雅编辑 郭琛校对 王心点击下图进入"全国新型冠状病毒感染肺炎实时地图"值班编辑吾彦祖聚焦肺炎疫情：可能存在持续人传人，武汉市长呼吁减少人员流动武汉公交地铁今日停运，机场火车站离汉通道关闭从SARS到新型肺炎：有些人怎么就戒不掉这口“野味”?本文未经新京报书面授权不得转载使用欢迎朋友圈分享。
